  <summary date="2019-02-26T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">VA Health Center Management Stability and Improvement Act

This bill directs the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) to develop and implement a plan to hire a director for each VA medical center without a permanent director.

Hiring priority shall be given to medical centers that have not had a permanent director for the longest periods.</summary>
